description: The mission of the museum is to inspire and facilitate the study of the ancient world by providing faculty and students access to a remarkable collection of archaeological artifacts.  The museum is dedicated to:The preservation of the collectionMuseum quality display and exhibitionsThe accessibility of the collection for teaching, study and research by faculty and studentsInterdisciplinary and collaborative research
